        @NotEmpty(message="The service ID cannot be empty")
protected @NotEmpty(message="The service ID cannot be empty") String serviceId
        ID of the service for which the rule takes effect. In weighted routing mode, ServiceId indicates the ServiceId of service provider, If this parameter is not configured, ServiceId takes effect for all Service parties
